title: Doctor Who - Big Finish Directors Podlet 01 - The Haunting of Th
description:
Doctor Who - Big Finish Directors Podlet 01 - The Haunting of Thomas Brewster

Well here&#039;s a cool new thing from Big Finish.   Released today is their 1st every Director&#039;s Podlet, what they say is expected to be a new feature to go along with new Doctor Who Stories.   

In this Episode #01, we join director Barnaby Edwards whom chats about his work on The Haunting of Thomas Brewster. This is the first of what Big Finish says will be an ongoing series of Director&#039;s Podlets - informal companion pieces to individual releases.

Enjoy!
